{"tid":2206552,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"賴琦媛被爆搭上內地凸腩有米叔叔    豪歎法國菜晒鑽戒","createTime":"2020-09-17T14:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T11:12:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"22ed1867af85511d190d9cae34e3f1fa5936beb2","tid":2206552,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C1NwCss4owp8Y7gGNGO29A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/8f4fe330-f8c3-11ea-bdf9-11690d1e20a9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FC1NwCss4owp8Y7gGNGO29A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2F8f4fe330-f8c3-11ea-bdf9-11690d1e20a9&h=a0adbec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年21歲的落選港姐賴琦媛（Ivy）憑一張寸嘴獲封「寸嘴Ivy」之名，一直被指拜金兼愛黐富貴朋友想釣金龜的她，日前被拍得與一位內地凸腩有米叔叔攬腰搭膊夜遊中環，更大歎七道法國菜，賴琦媛更於社交網大晒美食，中指還戴有閃爆鑽戒，富貴迫人。兩人食完飯之後，雙雙登上價值約百萬的名車離開，有指兩人已於何文田豪宅同居！但有傳有米叔叔已有家室，營商的他經常中港兩邊走。<br />\n<br />\n賴琦媛2016年已晒過類似的鑽戒，並且於讀書時期經已相當富貴，更曾跟李彩華前男友潘啟翀相戀，而參選港姐期間已是非不斷，有指她曾整容及愛於內地結識富商，早前更拍到她獲中年男子駕駛60萬名車接送，期間她更與男友人在車上煲煙，之後隨手把煙頭掉出車外，事後她公開道歉兼自言會戒煙。"},{"pid":"3783a72f302272a36cc58824137b401b4791dd76","tid":2206552,"uid":321421,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"60萬<span class=\"red\">名車</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50aff781ed4126a4e75a271fb9f009b1da140c42","tid":2206552,"uid":257448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815c973db61b2aa22349c41d2130730703aa4769","tid":2206552,"uid":36378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T17:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"